description:
MB Laos is an online banking app that allows customer to conduct transactions from anywhere at anytime. Driven by technology advances, MB Laos is available for iOS and able to efficiently operate on device connected to the Internet.
To satisfy the banking needs of customers, MB Laos perform a number of outstanding functions as follows:
- Login setup and transaction confirmation by password or fingerprint, and verification code sent via SMS OTP or Smart OTP;  
- Inquiries: checking and savings account balance, loan and credit, transaction history, exchange rate, interest rate or ATM/ Branch’s location;         
- eKYC on App mobile banking MB Laos
- Transfer: internal transfer, cashin, cashout;    
- QR Pay with online and offline merchants;        
- Online shopping with exclusive deals and promotions;
- Smart connection to e-wallet for payment and shopping.       
 MB Laos frequently upgrade new versions featured by new useful functions to make the life simpler and easier.
